data.description: Situated in a desirable location, this condo offers easy access to NRG stadium, Medical center and highways. With it's elegant wood flooring, cozy carpeted bedrooms, and the security of a gated community, this condo offers the best of both comfort and style. The property has storage outside of the unit. The air conditioning system and AC ducts were replaced 2 years ago. All appliances, including the 60" television are included in the price. scheduling a viewing now and experience the charm that awaits you in the gated community condo.
